org.apache.ignite.spi

Interface IgniteSpiTimeoutObject


  • public interface IgniteSpiTimeoutObject
    Provides possibility to schedule delayed execution, see IgniteSpiContext.addTimeoutObject(IgniteSpiTimeoutObject).

    Note: all timeout objects are executed in single dedicated thread, so implementation of onTimeout() should not use time consuming and blocking method.
